I"d<p>Crypto traders use <strong>div</strong> as a short for <strong>divergence</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Divergences</strong> are a “level” indicator, they are too vague to justify opening of a position.</p>

<p>Still, they are an important aspect of technical analysis and can give you edge because of how easily they get missed or misinterpreted.</p>

